name: Cell C: Light + Dark
description: Light and Dark editions of Cell C, the third entry in the Cell series. 1360x680 pixels, 5.68 MB, 58 frames. Consists of C1 (Light) and C2 (Dark) which exist as separate pieces and can be sent to the collector as a bonus upon collection, if so desired. Made with Pico-8 and post-processed.
